metadata.name: "Bomber"
metadata.description:
Bomber A.K.A writer or someone who's make graffiti art.
I remember when Graffiti inspired me to draw before i know about illustration / digital art.
I love graffiti because it's culture , adrenaline , street art on public space.
--
to says back my messages of appreciation , this piece comes with "Thanks stamp" for everyone who place a value for this work.
